ygData.msgSnippet: I have died twice in Firiona Vie. I have had groupmates die a lot more trying to get through there (esp when on corpse recovery) It is possible Selo s is fast
ygData.messageBody:
I have died twice in Firiona Vie. I have had groupmates die a lot
more trying to get through there (esp when on corpse recovery) It is
possible Selo's is fast enough that you don't aggro stuff. I have generally
gone through as my enchanter, who has no movement speed increase :( IF I
can get a Spirit of Wolf, though (without bugging people too much. I don't
want to be one of those the druids are laughing at behind their hands)
I do, and I don't think I've ever gotten killed then.

I do know it is generally going through Firiona Vie that causes
my guildies to declare Kunark a deathtrap and head abck to
Antonica.
